---
interface Props {
  whatsappUrl: string;
  included: string[];
}
const { whatsappUrl, included } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="pricing" class="relative bg-neutral-950 text-white py-20 lg:py-32 px-6 sm:px-10 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern opacity-[0.03]"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-yellow-400/20 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -right-[10%] text-[20vw] font-black text-neutral-900 leading-none select-none pointer-events-none tracking-tighter" aria-hidden="true">
    Desde $299
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 scroll-reveal">
          <div class="w-8 h-px bg-yellow-400"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-yellow-400/80">Precio claro</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black leading-[0.95] tracking-tight scroll-reveal" style="--d:50ms">
          Un plan.<br/>Sin letra chica.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md scroll-reveal" style="--d:75ms">
          Esto es exactamente lo que vas a pagar, cuándo, y qué incluye.
        </p>

        <!-- Pricing table -->
        <div class="mt-10 border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/30 scroll-reveal" style="--d:100ms">
          <!-- Row: primeros 3 meses (destacado) -->
          <div class="px-6 py-6 bg-yellow-400/[0.04] border-b border-neutral-800">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-yellow-400 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Primeros 3 meses</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1.5">40% de descuento</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <span class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-gradient-lemon leading-none">$299</span>
                <span class="block text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1">USD/mes</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row: desde mes 4 -->
          <div class="px-6 py-5 border-b border-neutral-800">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-white text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Desde el mes 4</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1.5">Precio regular</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-white leading-none">$499</span>
                <span class="block text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1">USD/mes</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Row: setup -->
          <div class="px-6 py-5">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-white text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Setup</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1.5">Una sola vez</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-white leading-none">$400</span>
                <span class="block text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-1">USD</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Summary: al firmar + ahorro -->
        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 scroll-reveal" style="--d:150ms">
          <div class="border border-yellow-400/30 bg-yellow-400/[0.05] p-5">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-yellow-400/80 mb-2">Al firmar pagas</p>
            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-white">$699 <span class="text-xs text-neutral-500 font-medium">USD</span></p>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 mt-1.5">Setup + primer mes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/30 p-5">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-400 mb-2">Ahorro 3 meses</p>
            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-green-400">$600 <span class="text-xs text-neutral-500 font-medium">USD</span></p>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500 mt-1.5">vs. precio regular</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed scroll-reveal" style="--d:175ms">
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Sin contrato ni permanencia mínima.</span> Cancelas el mes que quieras.
        </p>

        <!-- Ad budget note -->
        <div class="mt-6 p-5 border border-neutral-800 scroll-reveal" style="--d:200ms">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500 mb-2">Además del plan</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">El presupuesto publicitario se paga directo en Instagram y Facebook, no a nosotros. Recomendamos partir desde $200 USD/mes — tú decides cuánto.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 scroll-reveal" style="--d:250ms">
          <a href={whatsappUrl} target="_blank" data-wa-cta id="pricing-cta" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-300 text-neutral-950 font-bold px-8 py-4 transition-all text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
            Hablemos 20 minutos
          </a>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-600 mt-3">Sin compromiso. Evaluamos si somos buen fit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="scroll-reveal" style="--d:100ms">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500 mb-8">Todo incluido</p>
          <ul class="space-y-0">
            {included.map((item, i) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4 py-4 border-b border-neutral-800/50">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-yellow-400/40 mt-0.5 shrink-0">{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span>
                <span class="text-neutral-300 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonio — glass flotante -->
        <div class="mt-12 scroll-reveal" style="--d:200ms">
          <div class="testimonial-glass p-7 relative">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-0.5 text-yellow-400 text-sm mb-4">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-[15px] leading-relaxed italic mb-6">
              "Lelemon ha sido una pieza fundamental en el desarrollo de mis negocios, tanto para mi estudio jurídico como para mi agencia. Los resultados en captación de clientes fueron positivos desde el primer mes, logrando concretar mis primeros tres clientes rápidamente. ¡Una plataforma totalmente recomendada por su efectividad!"
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-yellow-400">N</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white text-sm font-bold">Nicolás Valdés</p>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-xs">Abogado · teayudamoslaboral.cl · teayudamosfamilia.cl</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonial-glass {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    box-shadow:
      0 20px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .testimonial-glass:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow:
      0 25px 60px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .text-gradient-lemon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FACC15, #84CC16, #FACC15);
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    animation: gradientShift 5s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes gradientShift {
    0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
  }
</style>
